<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الشَّامِ مِنَ الْجُحْفَةِ وَمُهَلُّ أَهْلِ نَجْدٍ مِنْ قَرْنٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قَالَ فَقَالَ الْقَاسِمُ وَمُهَلُّ أَهْلِ الْيَمَنِ مِنْ يَلَمْلَمَ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَفِي الْبَابِ عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ وَجَابِرِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ وَعَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ عَمْرٍو<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيُقَالُ حَدِيثُ ابْنِ عُمَرَ حَسَنٌ صَحِيحٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>